# X9_AI_system CODEOWNERS
#
# 作用:PR 改了哪些文件,会自动指派对应的 owner 来 review。
# 配合 Branch Protection 中的 "Require review from Code Owners"。
#
# 语法参考:https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# 使用前:把所有 @your-github-username 替换成真实的 GitHub 用户名。

# ===== 兜底:任何文件改动都需要 Rocky 知道 =====
*                                @rocky-github-username

# ===== 后端 Python =====
/core/                           @rocky-github-username
/desktop/backend/                @rocky-github-username
/scrapers/                       @rocky-github-username

# ===== 前端 =====
/web/                            @frontend-lead-username
/web-user/                       @frontend-lead-username

# ===== 扩展 / 桌面 =====
/desktop/chrome-extension/       @desktop-lead-username
/desktop/desktop/                @desktop-lead-username

# ===== 基础设施 / 部署 / 数据库 =====
# 这些都必须 Rocky 亲自 review
/infra/                          @rocky-github-username
/.github/                        @rocky-github-username
**/migrate_v*.py                 @rocky-github-username
**/schema*.sql                   @rocky-github-username
**/docker-compose*.yml           @rocky-github-username
Dockerfile*                      @rocky-github-username
**/deploy*.ps1                   @rocky-github-username
**/db_init*.ps1                  @rocky-github-username

# ===== 安全敏感 =====
.env.shared.example              @rocky-github-username
.gitignore                       @rocky-github-username
**/auth*.py                      @rocky-github-username
**/oauth*.py                     @rocky-github-username

# ===== 团队文档 =====
/docs/team/                      @rocky-github-username
